DESCRIPTION: - You can lookup a certain character using 'cl' command. In the charlookup menu, you can check the card's statistics, their 3D and animated images, gen headboards, fan leaderboard and the card ID. The card ID is needed when submitting images for versions.
CHAR_NF_SENSITIVE: No character found, Its a case sensitive search
NORMAL_DESC: Displays original version of the card
ADD_FAN_PTS: Increase your fan points for the card
GIF_DESC: Displays GIF version of the card
NAME: Name
MODAL_TITLE: Enter the amount and currency name
CORRECT_EXAMPLE: Correct format examples: `10 wists`,`3 gems`,`5000 silvers`
